      "text": "# 生物 Demo-Ready 冲刺 1 实现计划\n\n> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.\n\n**Goal:** 让生物学科知识树在浏览器中可视化呈现，并接通 answer_logs → BKT 数据管道，为 demo 做好基础。\n\n**Architecture:** 不新建任何子系统。将已有的 sync 脚本接入 app 启动（单事务）、将已有的 `_update_adaptive_mastery` 接入 pipeline event handler、新增薄 REST 包装层为前端提供节点详情（前端无法直调 MCP，见 design F001 修订）。\n\n**Gate 1 R1 处置:** F001(design 已修订) / F002(单事务) / F003(settings 收敛) / F004(json_each+PG 兜底) / F005(SQLite fixture) / F006(保持 show model+AbortController) / F007(schema 重写)\n\n**Tech Stack:** FastAPI (async lifespan) / SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async) / Vue 3 + AntV G6 / PostgreSQL\n\n**Design:** `docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-design.md`\n\n---\n\n## 文件结构\n\n| 操作 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py:23-148` | lifespan 增加 knowledge.db → PG 同步 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py` | on_exam_published 增加 adaptive mastery 更新 |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py` | 启动同步服务（单事务） |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` | 增加 sync_da_kp_map 函数（flush-only） |\n| Modify | `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue` | 增强详情面板（课标/教材/真题） |\n| Modify | `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js` | 增加 getNodeDetail API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py` | 节点详情聚合服务 |\n| Create | `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py` | 同步测试 |\n| Create | `tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py` | pipeline 接通测试 |\n| Create | `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py` | 节点详情 API 测试 |\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 启动同步\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py:64-66` (lifespan, 在 create_all 之后添加)\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` (添加 sync_da_kp_map)\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 启动时 concept_graph_nodes 为空 → 触发全量同步\n- ✓ 启动时 concept_graph_nodes 已有数据 → 跳过（幂等）\n- ✓ knowledge.db 不存在 → 警告日志，不崩溃\n- ✓ sync_da_catalog 同步 156 DA 到 da_catalog_snapshot\n- ✓ sync_da_kp_map 从 DA concept_ids 写入 DaKnowledgePointMap\n- ✗ 同步失败后应用仍能启动（非致命）\n- ✗ 同步不应删除学校端自定义数据（当前无此场景，但验证 sync 只写骨架表）\n\n**边界条件:**\n- knowledge.db 文件不存在 → 期望: 警告日志，跳过同步，应用正常启动\n- knowledge.db 中 concepts 表为空 → 期望: 同步 0 行，不报错\n- 重复调用同步（应用重启）→ 期望: 幂等，数据一致\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 启动同步写入 concept_graph_nodes\n   - 入口: app lifespan 启动流程（通过 `sync_knowledge_on_startup` 函数直接调用验证）\n   - 反例: 如果不调用 sync_to_postgres，concept_graph_nodes 保持 0 行——本测试验证同步后行数 > 0\n   - 边界: knowledge.db 不存在 / concepts 表为空 / 重复同步\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py -v`\n\n2. sync_da_kp_map 写入 DaKnowledgePointMap\n   - 入口: `sync_da_kp_map(knowledge_db_path, db)` 直接调用\n   - 反例: 如果不从 DA concept_ids 提取映射，DaKnowledgePointMap 保持 0 行——本测试验证写入后行数 > 0\n   - 边界: DA 无 concept_ids / concept_id 不在 concept_graph_nodes 中\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py::test_sync_da_kp_map -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 写 sync_da_kp_map 函数**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` 末尾添加:\n\n```python\nasync def sync_da_kp_map(knowledge_db_path: str, db: \"AsyncSession\") -> int:\n    \"\"\"从 knowledge.db 同步 DA → 知识点映射到 DaKnowledgePointMap。\n\n    每个 DA 的 linked_concept_ids 展开为 (da_id, concept_id) 行。\n    \"\"\"\n    from sqlalchemy import select, delete\n    from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(knowledge_db_path)\n    try:\n        catalog = build_da_catalog_from_knowledge_db(conn)\n    finally:\n        conn.close()\n\n    # 全量替换\n    await db.execute(delete(DaKnowledgePointMap))\n\n    count = 0\n    for item in catalog:\n        for concept_id in (item.get(\"concept_ids\") or []):\n            db.add(DaKnowledgePointMap(\n                da_id=item[\"da_id\"],\n                knowledge_point_id=concept_id,\n                weight=1.0,\n            ))\n            count += 1\n\n    # 不 commit — 由 sync_knowledge_on_startup 统一提交（F002 单事务）\n    await db.flush()\n    return count\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 创建 sync_service.py（单事务封装）**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py` 创建:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 同步服务（app 启动时调用）。\"\"\"\nimport logging\nimport re\nimport sqlite3\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport sqlalchemy as sa\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n# F003: 路径从 settings 读取，不硬编码\n_MODULE_RE = re.compile(r\"_M(\\d+)_\")\n\n\ndef _read_knowledge_db(db_path: str) -> tuple[list[dict], list[dict]]:\n    \"\"\"读取 knowledge.db 的 concepts 和 concept_relations。\"\"\"\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path)\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n    nodes = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts\"):\n        m = _MODULE_RE.search(row[\"id\"])\n        nodes.append({\n            \"id\": row[\"id\"], \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n            \"knowledge_level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            \"primary_module\": f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\",\n            \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n        })\n    edges = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT source_id, target_id, relation_type, strength, confidence FROM concept_relations\"\n    ):\n        edges.append({\n            \"source_id\": row[\"source_id\"], \"target_id\": row[\"target_id\"],\n            \"relation_type\": row[\"relation_type\"],\n            \"strength\": row[\"strength\"] or 1.0, \"confidence\": row[\"confidence\"] or 1.0,\n        })\n    conn.close()\n    return nodes, edges\n\n\nasync def _sync_graph(db: AsyncSession, nodes: list[dict], edges: list[dict]) -> None:\n    \"\"\"写入图谱数据（仅 flush，不 commit — F002 单事务）。\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphEdge))\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphNode))\n    for n in nodes:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphNode(\n            id=n[\"id\"], name=n[\"name\"], knowledge_level=n[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            primary_module=n[\"primary_module\"], description=n[\"description\"], synced_at=now,\n        ))\n    await db.flush()\n    for e in edges:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphEdge(\n            source_id=e[\"source_id\"], target_id=e[\"target_id\"],\n            relation_type=e[\"relation_type\"], strength=e[\"strength\"],\n            confidence=e[\"confidence\"], synced_at=now,\n        ))\n    await db.flush()  # F002: 不 commit，由 sync_knowledge_on_startup 统一提交\n\n\nasync def sync_knowledge_on_startup(db: AsyncSession, knowledge_db_path: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"启动时同步 knowledge.db → PostgreSQL（幂等：已有数据则跳过）。\n\n    同步内容:\n    1. concept_graph_nodes + edges（知识图谱结构）\n    2. da_catalog_snapshot（DA 目录）\n    3. da_knowledge_point_map（DA → 概念映射）\n\n    Returns: {\"status\": \"synced\"|\"skipped\"|\"not_found\", \"nodes\": int, \"edges\": int, \"das\": int, \"kp_map\": int}\n    \"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.config import settings\n    path = Path(knowledge_db_path) if knowledge_db_path else Path(settings.KNOWLEDGE_DB_PATH)  # F003\n    if not path.exists():\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db not found at %s\", path)\n        return {\"status\": \"not_found\"}\n\n    count_result = await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))\n    existing = count_result.scalar() or 0\n    if existing > 0:\n        logger.debug(\"sync: knowledge graph already populated (%d nodes), skipping\", existing)\n        return {\"status\": \"skipped\", \"nodes\": existing}\n\n    # 1. 图谱同步\n    nodes, edges = _read_knowledge_db(str(path))\n    await _sync_graph(db, nodes, edges)\n    logger.info(\"sync: knowledge graph → PG (%d nodes, %d edges)\", len(nodes), len(edges))\n\n    # 2. DA 目录 + DA-KP 映射\n    from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.sync import sync_da_catalog, sync_da_kp_map\n    da_count = await sync_da_catalog(str(path), db)\n    kp_count = await sync_da_kp_map(str(path), db)\n    logger.info(\"sync: DA catalog → PG (%d DAs, %d KP mappings)\", da_count, kp_count)\n\n    # F002: 三类投影统一单次 commit\n    await db.commit()\n    return {\"status\": \"synced\", \"nodes\": len(nodes), \"edges\": len(edges), \"das\": da_count, \"kp_map\": kp_count}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 在 app lifespan 中调用 sync**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` 的 lifespan 中，`logger.info(\"database tables created\")` 之后添加:\n\n```python\n    # Sync knowledge.db → PostgreSQL (idempotent, non-fatal)\n    try:\n        async with async_session() as db:\n            from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n            sync_result = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db)\n            if sync_result[\"status\"] == \"synced\":\n                logger.info(\n                    \"sync: knowledge.db → PG complete (%d nodes, %d edges, %d DAs, %d KP maps)\",\n                    sync_result[\"nodes\"], sync_result[\"edges\"], sync_result[\"das\"], sync_result[\"kp_map\"],\n                )\n    except Exception as e:\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db sync failed (non-fatal): %s\", e)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py`（F005: SQLite fixture，无宿主依赖）:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"启动同步测试（临时 SQLite fixture，不依赖本机 knowledge.db）。\"\"\"\nimport sqlite3, pytest\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaCatalogSnapshot, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n\ndef _create_test_knowledge_db(path: str):\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(path)\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE concepts (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, knowledge_level TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE concept_relations (source_id TEXT, target_id TEXT, relation_type TEXT, strength REAL, confidence REAL)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE diagnostic_attributes (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, linked_concept_ids TEXT, observable_behaviors TEXT, common_cause_families TEXT, required_evidence_modes TEXT, common_errors TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE study_units (id TEXT PK, linked_da_ids TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_A','TestA','L1','d')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_B','TestB','L1','d')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concept_relations VALUES ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_A','BIO_SR_CP_M1_B','prerequisite_hard',1.0,1.0)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO diagnostic_attributes VALUES ('da:bio_sr:m1_001','DA1','[\\\"BIO_SR_CP_M1_A\\\"]','[\\\"can id\\\"]','[\\\"gap\\\"]','[\\\"recall\\\"]','[]','d')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO study_units VALUES ('su:m1_001','[\\\"da:bio_sr:m1_001\\\"]')\")\n    conn.commit(); conn.close()\n\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef knowledge_db_path(tmp_path):\n    p = str(tmp_path / \"knowledge.db\"); _create_test_knowledge_db(p); return p\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_all_tables(db_session, knowledge_db_path):\n    \"\"\"F005: 单事务同步后 4 张表都有数据（确定性 fixture，无 skip）。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    r = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=knowledge_db_path)\n    assert r[\"status\"] == \"synced\"\n    assert r[\"nodes\"] == 2\n    assert r[\"edges\"] == 1\n    assert (await db_session.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))).scalar() == 2\n    assert (await db_session.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaKnowledgePointMap))).scalar() == 1\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_idempotent(db_session, knowledge_db_path):\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=knowledge_db_path)\n    r2 = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=knowledge_db_path)\n    assert r2[\"status\"] == \"skipped\"\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_missing_db(db_session):\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    assert (await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=\"/no.db\"))[\"status\"] == \"not_found\"\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py -v`\nExpected: 3 PASS（全部确定性，无 skip）\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/api/app.py \\\n        tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: knowledge.db → PG 启动同步（concept graph + DA catalog + DA-KP map）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: 接通 answer_logs → BKT 管道\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py:11-33`\n- Create: `tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ exam.published 事件触发 _update_adaptive_mastery\n- ✓ 幂等：同一考试重复触发不重复写入（AnswerLog 唯一约束）\n- ✓ 现有 update_knowledge_mastery 和 update_error_patterns 不受影响\n- ✗ _update_adaptive_mastery 失败不应阻塞其他流水线步骤\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 考试无题目 → 期望: _update_adaptive_mastery 返回 0，不报错\n- 学生缺考（is_absent=True）→ 期望: 跳过该学生\n- 同一考试重复发布 → 期望: AnswerLog 幂等，不重复插入\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. pipeline 事件触发 adaptive mastery 更新\n   - 入口: `on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": ..., \"school_id\": ...})` 事件处理\n   - 反例: 不调用 _update_adaptive_mastery 则 answer_logs 保持 0 行——本测试验证调用后有数据\n   - 边界: 无题目考试 / 缺考学生 / 重复触发\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 修改 pipeline/__init__.py**\n\n将 `on_exam_published` 函数修改为:\n\n```python\n@event_bus.on(\"exam.published\")\nasync def on_exam_published(payload: dict) -> None:\n    \"\"\"成绩发布后触发完整流水线（知识点掌握度 + 错误模式 + DA 自适应）。\"\"\"\n    exam_id = payload.get(\"exam_id\")\n    school_id = payload.get(\"school_id\")\n    if not exam_id or not school_id:\n        logger.warning(\"on_exam_published: missing exam_id or school_id\")\n        return\n\n    from edu_cloud.database import async_session\n    from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service import (\n        update_knowledge_mastery, update_error_patterns, _update_adaptive_mastery,\n    )\n\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        mastery = await update_knowledge_mastery(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        patterns = await update_error_patterns(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        await db.commit()  # 先提交已有步骤，保证不被 adaptive 失败阻塞\n        # adaptive 失败不阻塞已有流水线（R5 finding）\n        adaptive = 0\n        try:\n            adaptive = await _update_adaptive_mastery(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n            await db.commit()\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.warning(\"_update_adaptive_mastery failed (non-fatal): %s\", e)\n    logger.info(\n        \"on_exam_published: exam=%s, mastery=%d, patterns=%d, adaptive=%d\",\n        exam_id, mastery, patterns, adaptive,\n    )\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"验证 exam.published 事件触发 adaptive mastery 更新。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom unittest.mock import AsyncMock, patch\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_on_exam_published_calls_adaptive_mastery():\n    \"\"\"on_exam_published 应调用 _update_adaptive_mastery。\"\"\"\n    with patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service._update_adaptive_mastery\", new_callable=AsyncMock) as mock_adaptive, \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service.update_knowledge_mastery\", new_callable=AsyncMock, return_value=0), \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service.update_error_patterns\", new_callable=AsyncMock, return_value=0), \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.database.async_session\") as mock_session_factory:\n\n        mock_adaptive.return_value = 10\n\n        mock_db = AsyncMock()\n        mock_ctx = AsyncMock()\n        mock_ctx.__aenter__ = AsyncMock(return_value=mock_db)\n        mock_ctx.__aexit__ = AsyncMock(return_value=False)\n        mock_session_factory.return_value = mock_ctx\n\n        from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline import on_exam_published\n        await on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": \"test-exam\", \"school_id\": \"test-school\"})\n\n        mock_adaptive.assert_called_once_with(mock_db, exam_id=\"test-exam\", school_id=\"test-school\")\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_on_exam_published_missing_payload():\n    \"\"\"缺少 exam_id 或 school_id 时应直接返回。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline import on_exam_published\n    # 不应抛异常\n    await on_exam_published({})\n    await on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": \"x\"})\n    await on_exam_published({\"school_id\": \"x\"})\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py -v`\nExpected: PASS\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py \\\n        tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: 接通 answer_logs → BKT 管道（exam.published → _update_adaptive_mastery）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: 节点详情聚合 API\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py`\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` (添加 GET /graph/{node_id}/detail)\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 返回课标、教材锚点、关联 DA、典型真题（全部从 knowledge.db 查）\n- ✓ 有学情时返回班级掌握率\n- ✓ knowledge.db 不可用时优雅降级（返回部分数据）\n- ✗ 节点 ID 不存在 → 404\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 节点 ID 不存在 → 期望: HTTP 404\n- knowledge.db 不可用 → 期望: 返回 PG 中已有数据，knowledge.db 字段为空列表\n- 节点无关联 DA → 期望: da_list 为空列表，不报错\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 节点详情 API 返回结构化数据\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph/{node_id}/detail`\n   - 反例: 不查 knowledge.db 则 curriculum/textbook/questions 全为空——本测试验证有数据时字段非空\n   - 边界: 不存在的 node_id / knowledge.db 不可用\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 创建 detail_service.py**\n\n`src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"节点详情聚合 — 从 knowledge.db 查询课标/教材/DA/真题。\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport logging\nimport sqlite3\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nfrom edu_cloud.config import settings\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\ndef get_node_detail(node_id: str, *, pg_node: dict | None = None, knowledge_db_path: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"查询概念节点详情（F004: PG 兜底 + json_each 精确匹配）。\n\n    Args:\n        pg_node: PG 中已查到的节点基础信息（路由层传入，兜底用）\n    \"\"\"\n    base_concept = pg_node or {\"id\": node_id}\n    result = {\"concept\": base_concept, \"curriculum\": [], \"textbook\": [], \"das\": [], \"questions\": {}}\n\n    path = Path(knowledge_db_path) if knowledge_db_path else Path(settings.KNOWLEDGE_DB_PATH)\n    if not path.exists():\n        return result  # F004: 返回 PG 兜底信息，不丢失 name/description\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(str(path))\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n\n    # F004: 不重新初始化 result — 保留 PG 兜底的 base_concept\n\n    # 1. 概念基本信息（knowledge.db 有则覆盖 PG 兜底）\n    row = conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts WHERE id = ?\", (node_id,)).fetchone()\n    if row:\n        # R5: 统一 schema — 用 PG 字段名 level/module（前端期望）\n        from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import _MODULE_RE\n        m = _MODULE_RE.search(row[\"id\"])\n        result[\"concept\"] = {\n            \"id\": row[\"id\"], \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n            \"level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            \"module\": f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\",\n            \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n        }\n\n    # 2. 关联 DA（json_each 精确匹配，F004 修复）\n    das = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        SELECT da.id, da.name, da.observable_behaviors, da.common_cause_families\n        FROM diagnostic_attributes da, json_each(da.linked_concept_ids) je\n        WHERE je.value = ?\n    \"\"\", (node_id,)).fetchall()\n    result[\"das\"] = []\n    for da in das:\n        linked = json.loads(da[\"observable_behaviors\"]) if da[\"observable_behaviors\"] else []\n        result[\"das\"].append({\n            \"da_id\": da[\"id\"], \"name\": da[\"name\"],\n            \"observable_behaviors\": linked,\n        })\n\n    # 3. 课标要求（通过 DA → seed_req_da_map → curriculum_requirements）\n    da_ids = [d[\"da_id\"] for d in result[\"das\"]]\n    if da_ids:\n        placeholders = \",\".join(\"?\" * len(da_ids))\n        reqs = conn.execute(f\"\"\"\n            SELECT DISTINCT cr.id, cr.content\n            FROM curriculum_requirements cr\n            JOIN seed_req_da_map srdm ON srdm.requirement_id = cr.id\n            WHERE srdm.da_id IN ({placeholders})\n        \"\"\", da_ids).fetchall()\n        result[\"curriculum\"] = [{\"requirement_id\": r[\"id\"], \"content\": r[\"content\"]} for r in reqs]\n\n    # 4. 教材定位（通过概念名在 content_blocks 中搜索）\n    if row:\n        concept_name = row[\"name\"]\n        textbook_rows = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n            SELECT s.title AS section_title, d.title AS book\n            FROM content_blocks cb\n            JOIN sections s ON cb.section_id = s.id\n            JOIN documents d ON s.document_id = d.id\n            WHERE cb.content LIKE ? AND d.doc_type = 'textbook'\n            LIMIT 5\n        \"\"\", (f'%{concept_name}%',)).fetchall()\n        result[\"textbook\"] = [{\"section_title\": r[\"section_title\"], \"book\": r[\"book\"]} for r in textbook_rows]\n\n    # 5. 典型真题（通过 Q-Matrix DA 映射，按 transfer_band 分组，每组 3 题）\n    if da_ids:\n        for band in (\"near\", \"mid\", \"far\"):\n            items = conn.execute(f\"\"\"\n                SELECT DISTINCT ai.id, ai.stem, ai.answer, ai.question_type\n                FROM q_matrix qm\n                JOIN assessment_items ai ON qm.item_id = ai.id\n                WHERE qm.attribute_id IN ({placeholders})\n                  AND qm.transfer_band = ?\n                LIMIT 3\n            \"\"\", [*da_ids, band]).fetchall()\n            result[\"questions\"][band] = [\n                {\"id\": i[\"id\"], \"stem\": i[\"stem\"][:200], \"answer\": i[\"answer\"], \"type\": i[\"question_type\"]}\n                for i in items\n            ]\n\n    conn.close()\n    return result\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 添加路由**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` 添加:\n\n```python\n@router.get(\"/graph/{node_id}/detail\")\nasync def get_node_detail_endpoint(\n    node_id: str,\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),\n    current: dict = Depends(require_permission(\"VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE\")),  # F006: 沿用现有权限模式\n):\n    \"\"\"获取概念节点详情（课标/教材/DA/真题）。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode\n    node = (await db.execute(select(ConceptGraphNode).where(ConceptGraphNode.id == node_id))).scalar_one_or_none()\n    if not node:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail=\"Node not found\")\n\n    pg_node = {\"id\": node.id, \"name\": node.name, \"level\": node.knowledge_level,\n               \"module\": node.primary_module, \"description\": node.description}\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    return get_node_detail(node_id, pg_node=pg_node)  # F004: PG 兜底\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"节点详情服务测试。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_missing_db():\n    \"\"\"knowledge.db 不存在时返回空结构。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    result = get_node_detail(\"FAKE_NODE\", knowledge_db_path=\"/nonexistent.db\")\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"id\"] == \"FAKE_NODE\"\n    assert result[\"curriculum\"] == []\n    assert result[\"das\"] == []\n    assert result[\"questions\"] == {}\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_with_fixture(tmp_path):\n    \"\"\"F005: 用 SQLite fixture 验证 json_each 精确匹配（无宿主依赖）。\"\"\"\n    import sqlite3\n    db_path = str(tmp_path / \"test.db\")\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path)\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE concepts (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, knowledge_level TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE diagnostic_attributes (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, linked_concept_ids TEXT, observable_behaviors TEXT, common_cause_families TEXT, required_evidence_modes TEXT, common_errors TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE curriculum_requirements (id TEXT PK, content TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE seed_req_da_map (requirement_id TEXT, da_id TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE content_blocks (id TEXT PK, section_id TEXT, content TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE sections (id TEXT PK, title TEXT, document_id TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE documents (id TEXT PK, title TEXT, doc_type TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE q_matrix (item_id TEXT, attribute_id TEXT, transfer_band TEXT, required INT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE assessment_items (id TEXT PK, stem TEXT, answer TEXT, question_type TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('NODE_A','TestA','L1','desc')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO diagnostic_attributes VALUES ('da_1','DA1','[\\\"NODE_A\\\"]','[\\\"can id\\\"]','[]','[]','[]','d')\")\n    conn.commit(); conn.close()\n\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    result = get_node_detail(\"NODE_A\", knowledge_db_path=db_path)\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"name\"] == \"TestA\"\n    assert len(result[\"das\"]) == 1\n    assert result[\"das\"][0][\"da_id\"] == \"da_1\"\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_pg_fallback():\n    \"\"\"F004: knowledge.db 不存在时保留 PG 节点信息。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    pg = {\"id\": \"X\", \"name\": \"PG Name\", \"level\": \"L1\", \"module\": \"M1\"}\n    result = get_node_detail(\"X\", pg_node=pg, knowledge_db_path=\"/no.db\")\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"name\"] == \"PG Name\"  # PG 数据保留，不丢失\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py -v`\nExpected: 3 PASS（全部确定性，无 skip）\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py \\\n        tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: 节点详情聚合 API（课标/教材/DA/真题，从 knowledge.db 查询）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: 前端节点详情面板增强\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue`\n- Modify: `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 点击节点 → 调用 /graph/{node_id}/detail → 渲染课标/教材/DA/真题\n- ✓ 数据加载中显示 loading 状态\n- ✓ API 失败时优雅降级（显示已有的基础信息）\n- ✗ 真题 stem 超长时截断显示\n\n**边界条件:**\n- API 返回空列表 → 期望: 显示\"暂无数据\"占位\n- 网络错误 → 期望: 显示错误提示，不崩溃\n- 快速切换节点 → 期望: 取消前一次请求，显示最新节点数据\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 添加 API 函数**\n\n在 `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js` 添加:\n\n```javascript\nexport function getNodeDetail(nodeId, signal) {  // F006: signal for AbortController\n  return client.get(`/knowledge-tree/graph/${nodeId}/detail`, { signal })\n}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 增强 NodeDetailDrawer.vue**\n\n在 NodeDetailDrawer.vue 中，添加数据获取和 Tab 面板渲染。核心变更:\n\n1. 在 `<script setup>` 中添加 detail 数据获取:\n```javascript\nimport { ref, watch } from 'vue'\nimport { getNodeDetail } from '../../api/knowledgeTree'\n\n// F006: 保持现有 defineModel('show') 接口，不改为 visible prop\nconst props = defineProps({ node: Object })\nconst show = defineModel('show', { type: Boolean })\nconst detail = ref(null)\nconst detailLoading = ref(false)\nlet abortController = null\nlet fetchSeq = 0  // 序号守卫：防止旧请求 finally 覆盖新请求状态\n\nwatch(() => props.node?.id, async (nodeId) => {\n  if (!nodeId) return\n  if (abortController) abortController.abort()\n  abortController = new AbortController()\n  const mySeq = ++fetchSeq  // 每次 watch 递增\n  detailLoading.value = true\n  detail.value = null\n  try {\n    const { data } = await getNodeDetail(nodeId, abortController.signal)\n    if (mySeq === fetchSeq) detail.value = data  // 只有最新请求写入\n  } catch (e) {\n    if (e.name !== 'CanceledError' && e.name !== 'AbortError') {\n      console.warn('Failed to load node detail:', e)\n    }\n  } finally {\n    if (mySeq === fetchSeq) detailLoading.value = false  // 只有最新请求关 loading\n  }\n})\n```\n\n2. 在模板中添加 NTabs 面板（概要 / 课标 / 教材 / DA / 真题）:\n```html\n<n-tabs type=\"line\" v-if=\"detail\">\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"curriculum\" tab=\"课标要求\">\n    <div v-for=\"req in detail.curriculum\" :key=\"req.requirement_id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      {{ req.content }}\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.curriculum.length\" description=\"暂无课标数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"textbook\" tab=\"教材定位\">\n    <div v-for=\"tb in detail.textbook\" :key=\"tb.section_title\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      <strong>{{ tb.book }}</strong> — {{ tb.section_title }}\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.textbook.length\" description=\"暂无教材数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"das\" tab=\"诊断属性\">\n    <div v-for=\"da in detail.das\" :key=\"da.da_id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      <strong>{{ da.name }}</strong>\n      <ul><li v-for=\"b in da.observable_behaviors\" :key=\"b\">{{ b }}</li></ul>\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.das.length\" description=\"暂无 DA 数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"questions\" tab=\"典型真题\">\n    <div v-for=\"band in ['near', 'mid', 'far']\" :key=\"band\">\n      <h4>{{ {near:'基础',mid:'中等',far:'拓展'}[band] }}</h4>\n      <div v-for=\"q in (detail.questions[band] || [])\" :key=\"q.id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n        <p>{{ q.stem }}</p>\n        <p class=\"answer\">答案: {{ q.answer }}</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!Object.keys(detail.questions).length\" description=\"暂无真题数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n</n-tabs>\n<n-spin v-if=\"detailLoading\" />\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 运行前端测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend && npx vitest run`\nExpected: 现有测试全部 PASS（新增组件变更不应破坏现有测试）\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue \\\n        frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js\ngit commit -m \"feat: 知识树节点详情面板（课标/教材/DA/真题 Tab 展示）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: 端到端验证\n\n**Files:** 无新建文件\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 后端启动后 concept_graph_nodes 有 1233+ 行（全部 L0+L1+L2 概念）\n- ✓ concept_graph_edges 有 335 行\n- ✓ da_catalog_snapshot 有 156 行\n- ✓ da_knowledge_point_map 有数据\n- ✓ 前端知识树页面渲染出节点\n- ✓ 点击节点显示详情面板\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 启动后端验证数据同步**\n\n```bash\n# 在 WSL 中启动后端\ncd /mnt/c/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud\npython -m uvicorn edu_cloud.api.app:create_app --factory --host 0.0.0.0 --port 9000\n```\n\n检查启动日志中应出现:\n```\nsync: knowledge graph → PG (1233 nodes, 335 edges)\nsync: DA catalog → PG (156 DAs, xxx KP mappings)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 验证 PostgreSQL 数据**\n\n```bash\n# 连接数据库验证\npython -c \"\nimport asyncio\nfrom edu_cloud.database import async_session\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaCatalogSnapshot, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\nasync def check():\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        nodes = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))).scalar()\n        edges = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphEdge))).scalar()\n        das = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaCatalogSnapshot))).scalar()\n        kp = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaKnowledgePointMap))).scalar()\n        print(f'Nodes: {nodes}, Edges: {edges}, DAs: {das}, KP maps: {kp}')\n        assert nodes >= 1200, f'Expected >=1200 nodes (L0+L1+L2=1233), got {nodes}'\n        assert edges >= 335, f'Expected >=335 edges, got {edges}'\n        assert das >= 156, f'Expected >=156 DAs, got {das}'\n        assert kp > 0, f'Expected >0 KP maps, got {kp}'\n        print('All checks passed!')\n\nasyncio.run(check())\n\"\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 验证前端知识树渲染**\n\n```bash\n# 启动前端\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend\npython ~/.claude/scripts/serve.py \"C:/Program Files/nodejs/npm.cmd\" run dev\n```\n\n打开 http://localhost:5273 → 登录(admin/123456) → 知识树页面 → 验证:\n1. 图谱渲染出节点和边\n2. 按模块筛选正常\n3. 点击节点显示详情面板（课标/教材/DA/真题 Tab）\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 运行全量测试确认无回归**\n\n```bash\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest --tb=short -q\n```\n\nExpected: 1582+ tests PASS，无 FAIL\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit（如有修正）**\n\n```bash\ngit add -u\ngit commit -m \"fix: 端到端验证修正\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Contract Pack\n\n```yaml\ncontract_pack:\n  invariants:\n    - id: INV-001\n      statement: \"sync_knowledge_on_startup 完成后 concept_graph_nodes 行数等于 knowledge.db concepts 行数\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py::test_sync_all_tables\"\n    - id: INV-002\n      statement: \"三类投影（graph + DA catalog + KP map）在单事务内原子提交，任一失败全部回滚\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py::test_sync_all_tables\"\n    - id: INV-003\n      statement: \"on_exam_published 事件处理链依次调用 update_knowledge_mastery + update_error_patterns + _update_adaptive_mastery\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py::test_on_exam_published_calls_adaptive_mastery\"\n    - id: INV-004\n      statement: \"detail_service DA 关联使用 json_each 精确匹配，不使用 LIKE 模糊匹配\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py::test_node_detail_with_fixture\"\n\n  counter_examples:\n    - id: CE-001\n      scenario: \"sync 在 graph flush 后 DA 写入前崩溃，导致 PG 有图谱无 DA 的半同步状态\"\n      tests_that_still_pass: \"test_sync_all_tables 同时检查 4 张表行数，半同步会导致 DA/KP 行数不匹配而 FAIL\"\n      mitigation: \"单事务设计保证原子性——所有 flush 在最后统一 commit\"\n    - id: CE-002\n      scenario: \"detail_service 用 LIKE 匹配 DA，concept ID 前缀重合（如 M1_CELL 匹配到 M1_CELL_MEMBRANE）导致返回无关 DA\"\n      tests_that_still_pass: \"test_node_detail_pg_fallback 不检查 DA 准确性\"\n      mitigation: \"使用 json_each 精确展开匹配；test_node_detail_with_fixture 验证结果相关性\"\n    - id: CE-003\n      scenario: \"前端快速切换节点，旧请求晚于新请求返回，覆盖新节点详情\"\n      tests_that_still_pass: \"后端测试不覆盖前端竞态\"\n      mitigation: \"AbortController 取消前一次请求 + fetchSeq 序号守卫防止 stale finally 覆盖状态；test_debt 记录前端竞态测试延期\"\n\n  risk_modules:\n    - module: \"src/edu_cloud/api/app.py\"\n      reason: \"启动生命周期变更——新增同步步骤可能延长启动时间或阻塞后续 seed\"\n    - module: \"src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py\"\n      reason: \"事件处理链变更——新增 _update_adaptive_mastery 步骤可能影响已有流水线执行时间\"\n    - module: \"src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py\"\n      reason: \"新增 public API 路由——权限和错误处理需与现有 get_graph/get_mastery 一致\"\n\n  test_debt:\n    - item: \"前端 NodeDetailDrawer API 集成和 AbortController 竞态测试\"\n      reason: \"当前项目前端测试（72 Vitest）主要覆盖纯逻辑组件，API 集成需 mock 服务端\"\n      deadline: 2026-04-20\n    - item: \"INV-002 单事务回滚测试（注入 DA sync 失败后验证 graph 表也为空）\"\n      reason: \"SQLAlchemy async session 回滚行为依赖事务边界，需构造精确的异常注入 fixture\"\n      deadline: 2026-04-20\n```\n"
    }
  ],
  "structuredContent": {
    "content": "# 生物 Demo-Ready 冲刺 1 实现计划\n\n> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.\n\n**Goal:** 让生物学科知识树在浏览器中可视化呈现，并接通 answer_logs → BKT 数据管道，为 demo 做好基础。\n\n**Architecture:** 不新建任何子系统。将已有的 sync 脚本接入 app 启动（单事务）、将已有的 `_update_adaptive_mastery` 接入 pipeline event handler、新增薄 REST 包装层为前端提供节点详情（前端无法直调 MCP，见 design F001 修订）。\n\n**Gate 1 R1 处置:** F001(design 已修订) / F002(单事务) / F003(settings 收敛) / F004(json_each+PG 兜底) / F005(SQLite fixture) / F006(保持 show model+AbortController) / F007(schema 重写)\n\n**Tech Stack:** FastAPI (async lifespan) / SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async) / Vue 3 + AntV G6 / PostgreSQL\n\n**Design:** `docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-design.md`\n\n---\n\n## 文件结构\n\n| 操作 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py:23-148` | lifespan 增加 knowledge.db → PG 同步 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py` | on_exam_published 增加 adaptive mastery 更新 |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py` | 启动同步服务（单事务） |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` | 增加 sync_da_kp_map 函数（flush-only） |\n| Modify | `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue` | 增强详情面板（课标/教材/真题） |\n| Modify | `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js` | 增加 getNodeDetail API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py` | 节点详情聚合服务 |\n| Create | `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py` | 同步测试 |\n| Create | `tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py` | pipeline 接通测试 |\n| Create | `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py` | 节点详情 API 测试 |\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 启动同步\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py:64-66` (lifespan, 在 create_all 之后添加)\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` (添加 sync_da_kp_map)\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 启动时 concept_graph_nodes 为空 → 触发全量同步\n- ✓ 启动时 concept_graph_nodes 已有数据 → 跳过（幂等）\n- ✓ knowledge.db 不存在 → 警告日志，不崩溃\n- ✓ sync_da_catalog 同步 156 DA 到 da_catalog_snapshot\n- ✓ sync_da_kp_map 从 DA concept_ids 写入 DaKnowledgePointMap\n- ✗ 同步失败后应用仍能启动（非致命）\n- ✗ 同步不应删除学校端自定义数据（当前无此场景，但验证 sync 只写骨架表）\n\n**边界条件:**\n- knowledge.db 文件不存在 → 期望: 警告日志，跳过同步，应用正常启动\n- knowledge.db 中 concepts 表为空 → 期望: 同步 0 行，不报错\n- 重复调用同步（应用重启）→ 期望: 幂等，数据一致\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 启动同步写入 concept_graph_nodes\n   - 入口: app lifespan 启动流程（通过 `sync_knowledge_on_startup` 函数直接调用验证）\n   - 反例: 如果不调用 sync_to_postgres，concept_graph_nodes 保持 0 行——本测试验证同步后行数 > 0\n   - 边界: knowledge.db 不存在 / concepts 表为空 / 重复同步\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py -v`\n\n2. sync_da_kp_map 写入 DaKnowledgePointMap\n   - 入口: `sync_da_kp_map(knowledge_db_path, db)` 直接调用\n   - 反例: 如果不从 DA concept_ids 提取映射，DaKnowledgePointMap 保持 0 行——本测试验证写入后行数 > 0\n   - 边界: DA 无 concept_ids / concept_id 不在 concept_graph_nodes 中\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py::test_sync_da_kp_map -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 写 sync_da_kp_map 函数**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` 末尾添加:\n\n```python\nasync def sync_da_kp_map(knowledge_db_path: str, db: \"AsyncSession\") -> int:\n    \"\"\"从 knowledge.db 同步 DA → 知识点映射到 DaKnowledgePointMap。\n\n    每个 DA 的 linked_concept_ids 展开为 (da_id, concept_id) 行。\n    \"\"\"\n    from sqlalchemy import select, delete\n    from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(knowledge_db_path)\n    try:\n        catalog = build_da_catalog_from_knowledge_db(conn)\n    finally:\n        conn.close()\n\n    # 全量替换\n    await db.execute(delete(DaKnowledgePointMap))\n\n    count = 0\n    for item in catalog:\n        for concept_id in (item.get(\"concept_ids\") or []):\n            db.add(DaKnowledgePointMap(\n                da_id=item[\"da_id\"],\n                knowledge_point_id=concept_id,\n                weight=1.0,\n            ))\n            count += 1\n\n    # 不 commit — 由 sync_knowledge_on_startup 统一提交（F002 单事务）\n    await db.flush()\n    return count\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 创建 sync_service.py（单事务封装）**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py` 创建:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 同步服务（app 启动时调用）。\"\"\"\nimport logging\nimport re\nimport sqlite3\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport sqlalchemy as sa\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n# F003: 路径从 settings 读取，不硬编码\n_MODULE_RE = re.compile(r\"_M(\\d+)_\")\n\n\ndef _read_knowledge_db(db_path: str) -> tuple[list[dict], list[dict]]:\n    \"\"\"读取 knowledge.db 的 concepts 和 concept_relations。\"\"\"\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path)\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n    nodes = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts\"):\n        m = _MODULE_RE.search(row[\"id\"])\n        nodes.append({\n            \"id\": row[\"id\"], \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n            \"knowledge_level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            \"primary_module\": f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\",\n            \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n        })\n    edges = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT source_id, target_id, relation_type, strength, confidence FROM concept_relations\"\n    ):\n        edges.append({\n            \"source_id\": row[\"source_id\"], \"target_id\": row[\"target_id\"],\n            \"relation_type\": row[\"relation_type\"],\n            \"strength\": row[\"strength\"] or 1.0, \"confidence\": row[\"confidence\"] or 1.0,\n        })\n    conn.close()\n    return nodes, edges\n\n\nasync def _sync_graph(db: AsyncSession, nodes: list[dict], edges: list[dict]) -> None:\n    \"\"\"写入图谱数据（仅 flush，不 commit — F002 单事务）。\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphEdge))\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphNode))\n    for n in nodes:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphNode(\n            id=n[\"id\"], name=n[\"name\"], knowledge_level=n[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            primary_module=n[\"primary_module\"], description=n[\"description\"], synced_at=now,\n        ))\n    await db.flush()\n    for e in edges:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphEdge(\n            source_id=e[\"source_id\"], target_id=e[\"target_id\"],\n            relation_type=e[\"relation_type\"], strength=e[\"strength\"],\n            confidence=e[\"confidence\"], synced_at=now,\n        ))\n    await db.flush()  # F002: 不 commit，由 sync_knowledge_on_startup 统一提交\n\n\nasync def sync_knowledge_on_startup(db: AsyncSession, knowledge_db_path: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"启动时同步 knowledge.db → PostgreSQL（幂等：已有数据则跳过）。\n\n    同步内容:\n    1. concept_graph_nodes + edges（知识图谱结构）\n    2. da_catalog_snapshot（DA 目录）\n    3. da_knowledge_point_map（DA → 概念映射）\n\n    Returns: {\"status\": \"synced\"|\"skipped\"|\"not_found\", \"nodes\": int, \"edges\": int, \"das\": int, \"kp_map\": int}\n    \"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.config import settings\n    path = Path(knowledge_db_path) if knowledge_db_path else Path(settings.KNOWLEDGE_DB_PATH)  # F003\n    if not path.exists():\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db not found at %s\", path)\n        return {\"status\": \"not_found\"}\n\n    count_result = await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))\n    existing = count_result.scalar() or 0\n    if existing > 0:\n        logger.debug(\"sync: knowledge graph already populated (%d nodes), skipping\", existing)\n        return {\"status\": \"skipped\", \"nodes\": existing}\n\n    # 1. 图谱同步\n    nodes, edges = _read_knowledge_db(str(path))\n    await _sync_graph(db, nodes, edges)\n    logger.info(\"sync: knowledge graph → PG (%d nodes, %d edges)\", len(nodes), len(edges))\n\n    # 2. DA 目录 + DA-KP 映射\n    from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.sync import sync_da_catalog, sync_da_kp_map\n    da_count = await sync_da_catalog(str(path), db)\n    kp_count = await sync_da_kp_map(str(path), db)\n    logger.info(\"sync: DA catalog → PG (%d DAs, %d KP mappings)\", da_count, kp_count)\n\n    # F002: 三类投影统一单次 commit\n    await db.commit()\n    return {\"status\": \"synced\", \"nodes\": len(nodes), \"edges\": len(edges), \"das\": da_count, \"kp_map\": kp_count}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 在 app lifespan 中调用 sync**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` 的 lifespan 中，`logger.info(\"database tables created\")` 之后添加:\n\n```python\n    # Sync knowledge.db → PostgreSQL (idempotent, non-fatal)\n    try:\n        async with async_session() as db:\n            from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n            sync_result = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db)\n            if sync_result[\"status\"] == \"synced\":\n                logger.info(\n                    \"sync: knowledge.db → PG complete (%d nodes, %d edges, %d DAs, %d KP maps)\",\n                    sync_result[\"nodes\"], sync_result[\"edges\"], sync_result[\"das\"], sync_result[\"kp_map\"],\n                )\n    except Exception as e:\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db sync failed (non-fatal): %s\", e)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py`（F005: SQLite fixture，无宿主依赖）:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"启动同步测试（临时 SQLite fixture，不依赖本机 knowledge.db）。\"\"\"\nimport sqlite3, pytest\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaCatalogSnapshot, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n\ndef _create_test_knowledge_db(path: str):\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(path)\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE concepts (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, knowledge_level TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE concept_relations (source_id TEXT, target_id TEXT, relation_type TEXT, strength REAL, confidence REAL)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE diagnostic_attributes (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, linked_concept_ids TEXT, observable_behaviors TEXT, common_cause_families TEXT, required_evidence_modes TEXT, common_errors TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE study_units (id TEXT PK, linked_da_ids TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_A','TestA','L1','d')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_B','TestB','L1','d')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concept_relations VALUES ('BIO_SR_CP_M1_A','BIO_SR_CP_M1_B','prerequisite_hard',1.0,1.0)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO diagnostic_attributes VALUES ('da:bio_sr:m1_001','DA1','[\\\"BIO_SR_CP_M1_A\\\"]','[\\\"can id\\\"]','[\\\"gap\\\"]','[\\\"recall\\\"]','[]','d')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO study_units VALUES ('su:m1_001','[\\\"da:bio_sr:m1_001\\\"]')\")\n    conn.commit(); conn.close()\n\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef knowledge_db_path(tmp_path):\n    p = str(tmp_path / \"knowledge.db\"); _create_test_knowledge_db(p); return p\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_all_tables(db_session, knowledge_db_path):\n    \"\"\"F005: 单事务同步后 4 张表都有数据（确定性 fixture，无 skip）。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    r = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=knowledge_db_path)\n    assert r[\"status\"] == \"synced\"\n    assert r[\"nodes\"] == 2\n    assert r[\"edges\"] == 1\n    assert (await db_session.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))).scalar() == 2\n    assert (await db_session.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaKnowledgePointMap))).scalar() == 1\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_idempotent(db_session, knowledge_db_path):\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=knowledge_db_path)\n    r2 = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=knowledge_db_path)\n    assert r2[\"status\"] == \"skipped\"\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_missing_db(db_session):\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    assert (await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=\"/no.db\"))[\"status\"] == \"not_found\"\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py -v`\nExpected: 3 PASS（全部确定性，无 skip）\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/api/app.py \\\n        tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: knowledge.db → PG 启动同步（concept graph + DA catalog + DA-KP map）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: 接通 answer_logs → BKT 管道\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py:11-33`\n- Create: `tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ exam.published 事件触发 _update_adaptive_mastery\n- ✓ 幂等：同一考试重复触发不重复写入（AnswerLog 唯一约束）\n- ✓ 现有 update_knowledge_mastery 和 update_error_patterns 不受影响\n- ✗ _update_adaptive_mastery 失败不应阻塞其他流水线步骤\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 考试无题目 → 期望: _update_adaptive_mastery 返回 0，不报错\n- 学生缺考（is_absent=True）→ 期望: 跳过该学生\n- 同一考试重复发布 → 期望: AnswerLog 幂等，不重复插入\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. pipeline 事件触发 adaptive mastery 更新\n   - 入口: `on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": ..., \"school_id\": ...})` 事件处理\n   - 反例: 不调用 _update_adaptive_mastery 则 answer_logs 保持 0 行——本测试验证调用后有数据\n   - 边界: 无题目考试 / 缺考学生 / 重复触发\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 修改 pipeline/__init__.py**\n\n将 `on_exam_published` 函数修改为:\n\n```python\n@event_bus.on(\"exam.published\")\nasync def on_exam_published(payload: dict) -> None:\n    \"\"\"成绩发布后触发完整流水线（知识点掌握度 + 错误模式 + DA 自适应）。\"\"\"\n    exam_id = payload.get(\"exam_id\")\n    school_id = payload.get(\"school_id\")\n    if not exam_id or not school_id:\n        logger.warning(\"on_exam_published: missing exam_id or school_id\")\n        return\n\n    from edu_cloud.database import async_session\n    from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service import (\n        update_knowledge_mastery, update_error_patterns, _update_adaptive_mastery,\n    )\n\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        mastery = await update_knowledge_mastery(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        patterns = await update_error_patterns(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        await db.commit()  # 先提交已有步骤，保证不被 adaptive 失败阻塞\n        # adaptive 失败不阻塞已有流水线（R5 finding）\n        adaptive = 0\n        try:\n            adaptive = await _update_adaptive_mastery(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n            await db.commit()\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.warning(\"_update_adaptive_mastery failed (non-fatal): %s\", e)\n    logger.info(\n        \"on_exam_published: exam=%s, mastery=%d, patterns=%d, adaptive=%d\",\n        exam_id, mastery, patterns, adaptive,\n    )\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"验证 exam.published 事件触发 adaptive mastery 更新。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom unittest.mock import AsyncMock, patch\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_on_exam_published_calls_adaptive_mastery():\n    \"\"\"on_exam_published 应调用 _update_adaptive_mastery。\"\"\"\n    with patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service._update_adaptive_mastery\", new_callable=AsyncMock) as mock_adaptive, \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service.update_knowledge_mastery\", new_callable=AsyncMock, return_value=0), \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service.update_error_patterns\", new_callable=AsyncMock, return_value=0), \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.database.async_session\") as mock_session_factory:\n\n        mock_adaptive.return_value = 10\n\n        mock_db = AsyncMock()\n        mock_ctx = AsyncMock()\n        mock_ctx.__aenter__ = AsyncMock(return_value=mock_db)\n        mock_ctx.__aexit__ = AsyncMock(return_value=False)\n        mock_session_factory.return_value = mock_ctx\n\n        from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline import on_exam_published\n        await on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": \"test-exam\", \"school_id\": \"test-school\"})\n\n        mock_adaptive.assert_called_once_with(mock_db, exam_id=\"test-exam\", school_id=\"test-school\")\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_on_exam_published_missing_payload():\n    \"\"\"缺少 exam_id 或 school_id 时应直接返回。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline import on_exam_published\n    # 不应抛异常\n    await on_exam_published({})\n    await on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": \"x\"})\n    await on_exam_published({\"school_id\": \"x\"})\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py -v`\nExpected: PASS\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py \\\n        tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: 接通 answer_logs → BKT 管道（exam.published → _update_adaptive_mastery）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: 节点详情聚合 API\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py`\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` (添加 GET /graph/{node_id}/detail)\n- Create: `tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 返回课标、教材锚点、关联 DA、典型真题（全部从 knowledge.db 查）\n- ✓ 有学情时返回班级掌握率\n- ✓ knowledge.db 不可用时优雅降级（返回部分数据）\n- ✗ 节点 ID 不存在 → 404\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 节点 ID 不存在 → 期望: HTTP 404\n- knowledge.db 不可用 → 期望: 返回 PG 中已有数据，knowledge.db 字段为空列表\n- 节点无关联 DA → 期望: da_list 为空列表，不报错\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 节点详情 API 返回结构化数据\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph/{node_id}/detail`\n   - 反例: 不查 knowledge.db 则 curriculum/textbook/questions 全为空——本测试验证有数据时字段非空\n   - 边界: 不存在的 node_id / knowledge.db 不可用\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 创建 detail_service.py**\n\n`src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"节点详情聚合 — 从 knowledge.db 查询课标/教材/DA/真题。\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport logging\nimport sqlite3\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nfrom edu_cloud.config import settings\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\ndef get_node_detail(node_id: str, *, pg_node: dict | None = None, knowledge_db_path: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"查询概念节点详情（F004: PG 兜底 + json_each 精确匹配）。\n\n    Args:\n        pg_node: PG 中已查到的节点基础信息（路由层传入，兜底用）\n    \"\"\"\n    base_concept = pg_node or {\"id\": node_id}\n    result = {\"concept\": base_concept, \"curriculum\": [], \"textbook\": [], \"das\": [], \"questions\": {}}\n\n    path = Path(knowledge_db_path) if knowledge_db_path else Path(settings.KNOWLEDGE_DB_PATH)\n    if not path.exists():\n        return result  # F004: 返回 PG 兜底信息，不丢失 name/description\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(str(path))\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n\n    # F004: 不重新初始化 result — 保留 PG 兜底的 base_concept\n\n    # 1. 概念基本信息（knowledge.db 有则覆盖 PG 兜底）\n    row = conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts WHERE id = ?\", (node_id,)).fetchone()\n    if row:\n        # R5: 统一 schema — 用 PG 字段名 level/module（前端期望）\n        from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import _MODULE_RE\n        m = _MODULE_RE.search(row[\"id\"])\n        result[\"concept\"] = {\n            \"id\": row[\"id\"], \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n            \"level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            \"module\": f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\",\n            \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n        }\n\n    # 2. 关联 DA（json_each 精确匹配，F004 修复）\n    das = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        SELECT da.id, da.name, da.observable_behaviors, da.common_cause_families\n        FROM diagnostic_attributes da, json_each(da.linked_concept_ids) je\n        WHERE je.value = ?\n    \"\"\", (node_id,)).fetchall()\n    result[\"das\"] = []\n    for da in das:\n        linked = json.loads(da[\"observable_behaviors\"]) if da[\"observable_behaviors\"] else []\n        result[\"das\"].append({\n            \"da_id\": da[\"id\"], \"name\": da[\"name\"],\n            \"observable_behaviors\": linked,\n        })\n\n    # 3. 课标要求（通过 DA → seed_req_da_map → curriculum_requirements）\n    da_ids = [d[\"da_id\"] for d in result[\"das\"]]\n    if da_ids:\n        placeholders = \",\".join(\"?\" * len(da_ids))\n        reqs = conn.execute(f\"\"\"\n            SELECT DISTINCT cr.id, cr.content\n            FROM curriculum_requirements cr\n            JOIN seed_req_da_map srdm ON srdm.requirement_id = cr.id\n            WHERE srdm.da_id IN ({placeholders})\n        \"\"\", da_ids).fetchall()\n        result[\"curriculum\"] = [{\"requirement_id\": r[\"id\"], \"content\": r[\"content\"]} for r in reqs]\n\n    # 4. 教材定位（通过概念名在 content_blocks 中搜索）\n    if row:\n        concept_name = row[\"name\"]\n        textbook_rows = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n            SELECT s.title AS section_title, d.title AS book\n            FROM content_blocks cb\n            JOIN sections s ON cb.section_id = s.id\n            JOIN documents d ON s.document_id = d.id\n            WHERE cb.content LIKE ? AND d.doc_type = 'textbook'\n            LIMIT 5\n        \"\"\", (f'%{concept_name}%',)).fetchall()\n        result[\"textbook\"] = [{\"section_title\": r[\"section_title\"], \"book\": r[\"book\"]} for r in textbook_rows]\n\n    # 5. 典型真题（通过 Q-Matrix DA 映射，按 transfer_band 分组，每组 3 题）\n    if da_ids:\n        for band in (\"near\", \"mid\", \"far\"):\n            items = conn.execute(f\"\"\"\n                SELECT DISTINCT ai.id, ai.stem, ai.answer, ai.question_type\n                FROM q_matrix qm\n                JOIN assessment_items ai ON qm.item_id = ai.id\n                WHERE qm.attribute_id IN ({placeholders})\n                  AND qm.transfer_band = ?\n                LIMIT 3\n            \"\"\", [*da_ids, band]).fetchall()\n            result[\"questions\"][band] = [\n                {\"id\": i[\"id\"], \"stem\": i[\"stem\"][:200], \"answer\": i[\"answer\"], \"type\": i[\"question_type\"]}\n                for i in items\n            ]\n\n    conn.close()\n    return result\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 添加路由**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` 添加:\n\n```python\n@router.get(\"/graph/{node_id}/detail\")\nasync def get_node_detail_endpoint(\n    node_id: str,\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),\n    current: dict = Depends(require_permission(\"VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE\")),  # F006: 沿用现有权限模式\n):\n    \"\"\"获取概念节点详情（课标/教材/DA/真题）。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode\n    node = (await db.execute(select(ConceptGraphNode).where(ConceptGraphNode.id == node_id))).scalar_one_or_none()\n    if not node:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail=\"Node not found\")\n\n    pg_node = {\"id\": node.id, \"name\": node.name, \"level\": node.knowledge_level,\n               \"module\": node.primary_module, \"description\": node.description}\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    return get_node_detail(node_id, pg_node=pg_node)  # F004: PG 兜底\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"节点详情服务测试。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_missing_db():\n    \"\"\"knowledge.db 不存在时返回空结构。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    result = get_node_detail(\"FAKE_NODE\", knowledge_db_path=\"/nonexistent.db\")\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"id\"] == \"FAKE_NODE\"\n    assert result[\"curriculum\"] == []\n    assert result[\"das\"] == []\n    assert result[\"questions\"] == {}\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_with_fixture(tmp_path):\n    \"\"\"F005: 用 SQLite fixture 验证 json_each 精确匹配（无宿主依赖）。\"\"\"\n    import sqlite3\n    db_path = str(tmp_path / \"test.db\")\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path)\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE concepts (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, knowledge_level TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE diagnostic_attributes (id TEXT PK, name TEXT, linked_concept_ids TEXT, observable_behaviors TEXT, common_cause_families TEXT, required_evidence_modes TEXT, common_errors TEXT, description TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE curriculum_requirements (id TEXT PK, content TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE seed_req_da_map (requirement_id TEXT, da_id TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE content_blocks (id TEXT PK, section_id TEXT, content TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE sections (id TEXT PK, title TEXT, document_id TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE documents (id TEXT PK, title TEXT, doc_type TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE q_matrix (item_id TEXT, attribute_id TEXT, transfer_band TEXT, required INT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"CREATE TABLE assessment_items (id TEXT PK, stem TEXT, answer TEXT, question_type TEXT)\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO concepts VALUES ('NODE_A','TestA','L1','desc')\")\n    conn.execute(\"INSERT INTO diagnostic_attributes VALUES ('da_1','DA1','[\\\"NODE_A\\\"]','[\\\"can id\\\"]','[]','[]','[]','d')\")\n    conn.commit(); conn.close()\n\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    result = get_node_detail(\"NODE_A\", knowledge_db_path=db_path)\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"name\"] == \"TestA\"\n    assert len(result[\"das\"]) == 1\n    assert result[\"das\"][0][\"da_id\"] == \"da_1\"\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_pg_fallback():\n    \"\"\"F004: knowledge.db 不存在时保留 PG 节点信息。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    pg = {\"id\": \"X\", \"name\": \"PG Name\", \"level\": \"L1\", \"module\": \"M1\"}\n    result = get_node_detail(\"X\", pg_node=pg, knowledge_db_path=\"/no.db\")\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"name\"] == \"PG Name\"  # PG 数据保留，不丢失\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py -v`\nExpected: 3 PASS（全部确定性，无 skip）\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py \\\n        tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: 节点详情聚合 API（课标/教材/DA/真题，从 knowledge.db 查询）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: 前端节点详情面板增强\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue`\n- Modify: `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 点击节点 → 调用 /graph/{node_id}/detail → 渲染课标/教材/DA/真题\n- ✓ 数据加载中显示 loading 状态\n- ✓ API 失败时优雅降级（显示已有的基础信息）\n- ✗ 真题 stem 超长时截断显示\n\n**边界条件:**\n- API 返回空列表 → 期望: 显示\"暂无数据\"占位\n- 网络错误 → 期望: 显示错误提示，不崩溃\n- 快速切换节点 → 期望: 取消前一次请求，显示最新节点数据\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 添加 API 函数**\n\n在 `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js` 添加:\n\n```javascript\nexport function getNodeDetail(nodeId, signal) {  // F006: signal for AbortController\n  return client.get(`/knowledge-tree/graph/${nodeId}/detail`, { signal })\n}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 增强 NodeDetailDrawer.vue**\n\n在 NodeDetailDrawer.vue 中，添加数据获取和 Tab 面板渲染。核心变更:\n\n1. 在 `<script setup>` 中添加 detail 数据获取:\n```javascript\nimport { ref, watch } from 'vue'\nimport { getNodeDetail } from '../../api/knowledgeTree'\n\n// F006: 保持现有 defineModel('show') 接口，不改为 visible prop\nconst props = defineProps({ node: Object })\nconst show = defineModel('show', { type: Boolean })\nconst detail = ref(null)\nconst detailLoading = ref(false)\nlet abortController = null\nlet fetchSeq = 0  // 序号守卫：防止旧请求 finally 覆盖新请求状态\n\nwatch(() => props.node?.id, async (nodeId) => {\n  if (!nodeId) return\n  if (abortController) abortController.abort()\n  abortController = new AbortController()\n  const mySeq = ++fetchSeq  // 每次 watch 递增\n  detailLoading.value = true\n  detail.value = null\n  try {\n    const { data } = await getNodeDetail(nodeId, abortController.signal)\n    if (mySeq === fetchSeq) detail.value = data  // 只有最新请求写入\n  } catch (e) {\n    if (e.name !== 'CanceledError' && e.name !== 'AbortError') {\n      console.warn('Failed to load node detail:', e)\n    }\n  } finally {\n    if (mySeq === fetchSeq) detailLoading.value = false  // 只有最新请求关 loading\n  }\n})\n```\n\n2. 在模板中添加 NTabs 面板（概要 / 课标 / 教材 / DA / 真题）:\n```html\n<n-tabs type=\"line\" v-if=\"detail\">\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"curriculum\" tab=\"课标要求\">\n    <div v-for=\"req in detail.curriculum\" :key=\"req.requirement_id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      {{ req.content }}\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.curriculum.length\" description=\"暂无课标数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"textbook\" tab=\"教材定位\">\n    <div v-for=\"tb in detail.textbook\" :key=\"tb.section_title\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      <strong>{{ tb.book }}</strong> — {{ tb.section_title }}\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.textbook.length\" description=\"暂无教材数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"das\" tab=\"诊断属性\">\n    <div v-for=\"da in detail.das\" :key=\"da.da_id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      <strong>{{ da.name }}</strong>\n      <ul><li v-for=\"b in da.observable_behaviors\" :key=\"b\">{{ b }}</li></ul>\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.das.length\" description=\"暂无 DA 数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"questions\" tab=\"典型真题\">\n    <div v-for=\"band in ['near', 'mid', 'far']\" :key=\"band\">\n      <h4>{{ {near:'基础',mid:'中等',far:'拓展'}[band] }}</h4>\n      <div v-for=\"q in (detail.questions[band] || [])\" :key=\"q.id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n        <p>{{ q.stem }}</p>\n        <p class=\"answer\">答案: {{ q.answer }}</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!Object.keys(detail.questions).length\" description=\"暂无真题数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n</n-tabs>\n<n-spin v-if=\"detailLoading\" />\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 运行前端测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend && npx vitest run`\nExpected: 现有测试全部 PASS（新增组件变更不应破坏现有测试）\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue \\\n        frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js\ngit commit -m \"feat: 知识树节点详情面板（课标/教材/DA/真题 Tab 展示）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: 端到端验证\n\n**Files:** 无新建文件\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 后端启动后 concept_graph_nodes 有 1233+ 行（全部 L0+L1+L2 概念）\n- ✓ concept_graph_edges 有 335 行\n- ✓ da_catalog_snapshot 有 156 行\n- ✓ da_knowledge_point_map 有数据\n- ✓ 前端知识树页面渲染出节点\n- ✓ 点击节点显示详情面板\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 启动后端验证数据同步**\n\n```bash\n# 在 WSL 中启动后端\ncd /mnt/c/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud\npython -m uvicorn edu_cloud.api.app:create_app --factory --host 0.0.0.0 --port 9000\n```\n\n检查启动日志中应出现:\n```\nsync: knowledge graph → PG (1233 nodes, 335 edges)\nsync: DA catalog → PG (156 DAs, xxx KP mappings)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 验证 PostgreSQL 数据**\n\n```bash\n# 连接数据库验证\npython -c \"\nimport asyncio\nfrom edu_cloud.database import async_session\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaCatalogSnapshot, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\nasync def check():\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        nodes = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))).scalar()\n        edges = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphEdge))).scalar()\n        das = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaCatalogSnapshot))).scalar()\n        kp = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaKnowledgePointMap))).scalar()\n        print(f'Nodes: {nodes}, Edges: {edges}, DAs: {das}, KP maps: {kp}')\n        assert nodes >= 1200, f'Expected >=1200 nodes (L0+L1+L2=1233), got {nodes}'\n        assert edges >= 335, f'Expected >=335 edges, got {edges}'\n        assert das >= 156, f'Expected >=156 DAs, got {das}'\n        assert kp > 0, f'Expected >0 KP maps, got {kp}'\n        print('All checks passed!')\n\nasyncio.run(check())\n\"\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 验证前端知识树渲染**\n\n```bash\n# 启动前端\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend\npython ~/.claude/scripts/serve.py \"C:/Program Files/nodejs/npm.cmd\" run dev\n```\n\n打开 http://localhost:5273 → 登录(admin/123456) → 知识树页面 → 验证:\n1. 图谱渲染出节点和边\n2. 按模块筛选正常\n3. 点击节点显示详情面板（课标/教材/DA/真题 Tab）\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 运行全量测试确认无回归**\n\n```bash\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest --tb=short -q\n```\n\nExpected: 1582+ tests PASS，无 FAIL\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit（如有修正）**\n\n```bash\ngit add -u\ngit commit -m \"fix: 端到端验证修正\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Contract Pack\n\n```yaml\ncontract_pack:\n  invariants:\n    - id: INV-001\n      statement: \"sync_knowledge_on_startup 完成后 concept_graph_nodes 行数等于 knowledge.db concepts 行数\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py::test_sync_all_tables\"\n    - id: INV-002\n      statement: \"三类投影（graph + DA catalog + KP map）在单事务内原子提交，任一失败全部回滚\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_sync_startup.py::test_sync_all_tables\"\n    - id: INV-003\n      statement: \"on_exam_published 事件处理链依次调用 update_knowledge_mastery + update_error_patterns + _update_adaptive_mastery\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py::test_on_exam_published_calls_adaptive_mastery\"\n    - id: INV-004\n      statement: \"detail_service DA 关联使用 json_each 精确匹配，不使用 LIKE 模糊匹配\"\n      verification: pending_test\n      note: \"tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_node_detail_api.py::test_node_detail_with_fixture\"\n\n  counter_examples:\n    - id: CE-001\n      scenario: \"sync 在 graph flush 后 DA 写入前崩溃，导致 PG 有图谱无 DA 的半同步状态\"\n      tests_that_still_pass: \"test_sync_all_tables 同时检查 4 张表行数，半同步会导致 DA/KP 行数不匹配而 FAIL\"\n      mitigation: \"单事务设计保证原子性——所有 flush 在最后统一 commit\"\n    - id: CE-002\n      scenario: \"detail_service 用 LIKE 匹配 DA，concept ID 前缀重合（如 M1_CELL 匹配到 M1_CELL_MEMBRANE）导致返回无关 DA\"\n      tests_that_still_pass: \"test_node_detail_pg_fallback 不检查 DA 准确性\"\n      mitigation: \"使用 json_each 精确展开匹配；test_node_detail_with_fixture 验证结果相关性\"\n    - id: CE-003\n      scenario: \"前端快速切换节点，旧请求晚于新请求返回，覆盖新节点详情\"\n      tests_that_still_pass: \"后端测试不覆盖前端竞态\"\n      mitigation: \"AbortController 取消前一次请求 + fetchSeq 序号守卫防止 stale finally 覆盖状态；test_debt 记录前端竞态测试延期\"\n\n  risk_modules:\n    - module: \"src/edu_cloud/api/app.py\"\n      reason: \"启动生命周期变更——新增同步步骤可能延长启动时间或阻塞后续 seed\"\n    - module: \"src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py\"\n      reason: \"事件处理链变更——新增 _update_adaptive_mastery 步骤可能影响已有流水线执行时间\"\n    - module: \"src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py\"\n      reason: \"新增 public API 路由——权限和错误处理需与现有 get_graph/get_mastery 一致\"\n\n  test_debt:\n    - item: \"前端 NodeDetailDrawer API 集成和 AbortController 竞态测试\"\n      reason: \"当前项目前端测试（72 Vitest）主要覆盖纯逻辑组件，API 集成需 mock 服务端\"\n      deadline: 2026-04-20\n    - item: \"INV-002 单事务回滚测试（注入 DA sync 失败后验证 graph 表也为空）\"\n      reason: \"SQLAlchemy async session 回滚行为依赖事务边界，需构造精确的异常注入 fixture\"\n      deadline: 2026-04-20\n```\n"
